# Technical Architecture – SB Stocks

## Overview

The technical architecture of **SB Stocks** describes the technologies, frameworks, components, and communication flow used to build the application. The system follows a **three-tier architecture** with a **Model-View-Controller (MVC)** design pattern, ensuring scalability, modularity, security, and maintainability.

