# Communication Flow

```text
User
   │
   ▼
React Frontend
   │
Axios HTTP Request
   │
   ▼
Express REST API
   │
   ├── Authenticate User
   ├── Validate Request
   ├── Business Logic
   ├── Fetch Stock Data
   └── Update Portfolio
   │
   ▼
Database + External Stock API
   │
   ▼
JSON Response
   │
   ▼
React Updates User Interface
```

